Usulson  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ujzonn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jzonn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elite Poster</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(2/16/01 7:29:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=64.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Divine Legion Will Be in Hate Sat 1pm EST</span><hr size=1> If two guilds/groups become 'embroiled in nasty, ugly, and heated debate', that's the fault of the guild leaders for not stepping up and working something out.  Sorcha's post was exactly such a contact you said should be sought.  She didn't say, 'Hey...just wanted you to know we are changing our proposed Hate raid to match yours.  We want to make sure you are screwed over.'  She posted their intent and offered a location further discussion could be exchanged.  Could she have gone to your site and posted as well?  Sure.<br>
<br>
You're only in a position of being rushed because you think you are.  If you get up there and find three other groups already pulling (who could care less about posting an intent here), what are you going to do?  If you get up there and it's empty (completely--mobs and PCs), you'll have a lot of time to figure out your pace.<br>
<br>
Relax.  Don't worry about them other than to know you may have to pick and choose your targets. <p><B><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE=2 COLOR="#3A6EA5">Jzonn Stormwolf &lt;Final Destiny&gt;</B></FONT><BR>
<I><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE=2 COLOR="#cfcfcf">Ranger of Karana</I></FONT></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ujboone.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jboone</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>New to the block</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(2/16/01 8:19:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=64.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Divine Legion Will Be in Hate Sat 1pm EST</span><hr size=1> To the last reply i have contacted their boards just to get no response.. I want to work something out but am getting no response what so ever.. How do i work something out with a person who wont answer.. So now it looks like they just wanted to tell us hey were going up to. no working anything out. If they really wanted to work things out they would have responded on their boards am i not correct? <p>Booney (52nd Druid of Tunare)</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uhagusbruichladdich.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hagus Bruichladdich</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>New to the block</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(2/16/01 8:30:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=64.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/dannglenn/Hagus_256color.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Divine Legion Will Be in Hate Sat 1pm EST</span><hr size=1> Give it time Booney.  We still have a lot of time from now till break-in time.  We'll see how the events unfold when they unfold.  I'm not going to worry about it until there's something to worry about. <p>--Hagus Bruichladdich.
